{"title_page": "Pennsylvania Station (New York City)", "text_new": "{{About|the current intercity rail station in New York City|similarly named rail stations in other cities|Pennsylvania Station|the adjacent subway stations|34th Street\u2013Penn Station (IND Eighth Avenue Line)|and|34th Street\u2013Penn Station (IRT Broadway\u2013Seventh Avenue Line)|the original station|Pennsylvania Station (1910\u20131963)}}\n{{short description|Train station in New York City}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=May 2019}}\n{{Infobox station\n| name = Pennsylvania Station<br/><small>New York, NY</small>\n| style = Amtrak\n| type = [[Amtrak]] [[inter-city rail]] station <br>[[Long Island Rail Road]] [[commuter rail]] terminal <br>[[NJ Transit Rail Operations|NJ Transit]] commuter rail terminal\n| image = File:NYC Penn Station 7th Avenue Entrance 2013.jpg\n| caption = Entrance on Seventh Avenue by [[Penn Plaza]]\n| address = [[Seventh Avenue (Manhattan)|7th]] & [[Eighth Avenue (Manhattan)|8th]] Avenues, between [[31st Street (Manhattan)|31st]] & [[33rd Street (Manhattan)|33rd]] Streets<br>[[Manhattan]], [[New York City]]\n| owned = [[Amtrak]]\n| line = [[Northeast Corridor]], [[Empire Corridor]]\n| platform = 11 [[island platform]]s\n| tracks = 21\n| connections = :'''[[New York City Subway|MTA New York City Subway]]''':\n:{{NYCS Broadway-Seventh south|time=bullets}} at [[34th Street\u2013Penn Station (IRT Broadway\u2013Seventh Avenue Line)|34th Street\u2013Penn Station]] (7th Avenue)\n:{{NYCS Eighth south|time=bullets}} at [[34th Street\u2013Penn Station (IND Eighth Avenue Line)|34th Street\u2013Penn Station]] (8th Avenue)\n:{{NYCS Herald Square|time=bullets}} at [[34th Street\u2013Herald Square (New York City Subway)|34th Street\u2013Herald Square]]\n:{{rint|path|18px}} '''[[Port Authority Trans-Hudson|PATH]]''': [[JSQ\u201333]], [[HOB\u201333]], [[JSQ\u201333 (via HOB)]] (at [[33rd Street (PATH station)|33rd Street]])\n:{{bus icon|12px|Local Transit}} '''[[MTA Regional Bus Operations|MTA New 